# Software Design

## Software Modules

The firmware is divided into independent software modules.

- System Initialization
- Timer Configuration
- IR Sensor Interface
- Pulse Counter
- RPM Calculation
- LCD Driver
- System Monitoring
- Main Control Loop

## Software Operation

The firmware initializes all peripherals before entering an infinite execution loop.

During each sampling interval, the firmware counts sensor pulses, calculates RPM, updates the LCD, performs diagnostic checks, and prepares the system for the next measurement cycle.